Uses of Package
com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer

  • Packages that use com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer 
    Package Description
    com.noctarius.borabora.builder
    This package contains the basic builder classes for Parser (ParserBuilder), Query (QueryBuilder) and Writer (WriterBuilder).
    com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer
    This package contains the query optimizer SPI, which interface definitions are used to implement a query optimizer or a strategy on how to apply a set of query optimizers to a given query.
    com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.pipeline
    This package contains all interfaces required to either implement custom QueryStages or complete QueryPipeline implementations together with their according factories and the pipeline flow control VisitResult.
  • Classes in com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer used by com.noctarius.borabora.builder 
    Class and Description
    QueryOptimizer
    The QueryOptimizer interface defines a single optimizer strategy.
    QueryOptimizerStrategyFactory
    The QueryOptimizerStrategyFactory interface defines the factory to create an instance of a QueryOptimizerStrategy to apply rules and priorities specific to an implementation.
  • Classes in com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer used by com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer 
    Class and Description
    QueryOptimizer
    The QueryOptimizer interface defines a single optimizer strategy.
    QueryOptimizerStrategy
    The QueryOptimizerStrategy interface describes a strategy on how to apply different QueryOptimizers to optimize the actual query.
  • Classes in com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.optimizer used by com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.pipeline 
    Class and Description
    QueryOptimizerStrategy
    The QueryOptimizerStrategy interface describes a strategy on how to apply different QueryOptimizers to optimize the actual query.
